3. cs.DL (Digital Libraries) - Although the paper is not directly related to digital libraries, the EL family of description logics (DLs) mentioned in the paper is commonly used in digital libraries. 
4. cs.SE (Software Engineering) - The paper discusses the development of an efficient algorithm for group-MUS enumeration, which is a relevant topic in software engineering. 
5. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper proposes a new algorithm for group-MUS enumeration, which is a topic related to data structures and algorithms.
